Class Summary
DocumentStyleImpl A helper class to get computed CSS styles for elements.
DocumentStyleImplIE A helper class to get computed CSS styles for elements on IE6.
SelectorEngineImpl Base/Utility class for runtime selector engine implementations.
SelectorEngineImpl.Sequence Internal class.
SelectorEngineImpl.SplitRule Internal class.
SelectorEngineJS Runtime selector engine implementation with no-XPath/native support based on DOMAssistant.

SelectorEngineNative Runtime selector engine implementation for browsers with native querySelectorAll support.
SelectorEngineXPath Runtime selector engine implementation which translates selectors to XPath and delegates to document.evaluate().
